<p># DoughForge: The Reproducible Self-Publishing Desktop Kit</p>
<p>**By Roger G. Lewis**</p>
<p>*“No passion in the world is equal to the passion to alter someone
else’s draft.”*</p>
<p>— H. G. Wells</p>
